4bc2			; | READCONT (  -- u1  )  Pushes the READ continuation flag to stack | DONE 
4bc2			; | | If the most recent READ results in a full buffer load then this flag is set and will indicate that 
4bc2			; | | a further read should, if applicable, be CONCAT to the previous read. 
4bc2			; | | > [!NOTE] 
